metadata.title: P. Graham Dunn Better Together Red Birds 10 x 3.4 Pine Wood Decorative String Sign
features: Features sentiment reading "Better Together" with bird couple design; Weathered details give hope and inspiration along with a farmhouse chic flair

Decorative string sign measures approximately 10 x 3.4 x 0.4 inches; Jute string is attached to the back, creating signage that can easily be hung from knobs, handles, and hooks throughout the home

description: P. Graham Dunn is a family owned and operated business that opened its doors in 1976. Handcrafted character combined with modern computerized carving and laser operations, all based in the heart of Amish country in Dalton, Ohio, makes this company truly special. Today P. Graham Dunn serves over 4,000 accounts, most in the U.S., and the remainder in Canada and around the world. Features sentiment reading "Better Together" with bird couple design; Weathered details give hope and inspiration along with a farmhouse chic flair. Sign is constructed from a single pine wood slat; Features uplifting sentiment paired with weathered, farmhouse-inspired design. Decorative string sign measures approximately 10 x 3.4 x 0.4 inches; Jute string is attached to the back, creating signage that can easily be hung from knobs, handles, and hooks throughout the home.
